{"id":"2e378c9e-e914-4a23-91d9-e60d5453d7a5","name":"The Hunger Games RPG","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 162, 0);\"><strong><em>\"And may the odds.. be ever in your favor.\"</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 164, 55);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(47, 36, 21); color: inherit;\">Welcome to The Hunger games RPG. You may play as a Tribute, a Capitol citizen, a rebel, or Any role you'd like/want to be! You can start a Rebellion.. You can play in a game, You can do whatever you want in the Hunger games RPG!</mark></em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 210, 84);\"><strong>I recommend using my bots with proxy, gemini, deepseek, claude, etc! :)</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 121, 113);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(53, 50, 45); color: inherit;\">A creator note here since I've been getting into the hunger games lately again. There may be some Lore inaccuracies that are bound to happen when you rp BUT since this bot isn't exactly designed for canon roleplaying (you still can rp in a scenario or and with some characters that are canonwise [e.g katniss everdeen, etc.) There isn't a specific time period set with the bot so go nuts with it. You can play in the 10th hunger games, 45th, and the list goes on. You can do ANYTHING basically. That's all. Have fun :)</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 140, 181);\"><strong>Panem Districts to choose from.. (OPTIONAL)</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 54, 79);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(146, 143, 177); color: inherit;\">Capitol</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 42, 11);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(141, 121, 62); color: inherit;\">District 1</mark></strong></span><strong> — Luxury Goods</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(61, 38, 23);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(112, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">District 2</mark></strong></span><strong> — Masonry &amp; Weaponry</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 112, 58);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(53, 61, 22); color: inherit;\">District 3</mark></strong></span><strong> — Technology &amp; Electronics</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(42, 92, 70);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 42, 30); color: inherit;\">District 4</mark></strong></span><strong> — Fishing</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 148, 145);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(43, 74, 81); color: inherit;\">District 5</mark></strong></span><strong> — Power &amp; Electricity</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 134, 181);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(36, 69, 107); color: inherit;\">District 6</mark></strong></span><strong> — Transportation</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 71, 37);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 31, 15); color: inherit;\">District 7</mark></strong></span><strong> — Lumber &amp; Paper</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 47, 47);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(40, 9, 9); color: inherit;\">District 8</mark></strong></span><strong> — Textiles</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 53, 25);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(91, 99, 62); color: inherit;\">District 9</mark></strong></span><strong> — Grain.</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(151, 63, 86);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(81, 32, 53); color: inherit;\">District 10</mark></strong></span><strong> — Livestock</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 62, 166);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(31, 31, 93); color: inherit;\">District 11</mark></strong></span><strong> — Agriculture</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 34, 49);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(91, 45, 122); color: inherit;\">District 12</mark></strong></span><strong> — Coal Mining</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella